<li>Frank, John P., <i>The Justices of the United States Supreme Court: Their Lives and Major Opinions</i> (Leon Friedman and Fred L. Israel, editors) (Chelsea House Publishers, 1995) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0791013774" class="internal">ISBN 0791013774</a>, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780791013779" class="internal">ISBN 978-0791013779</a>.</li>
